function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.2.3') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.2.3!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.4.0') < 0) {
	err('You need at least PHP Version 7.4 to update to this version');
}

// Dir added: userdata/tenant
@mkdir('userdata/tenant');
if (!is_dir('userdata/tenant')) {
	warn('Directory could not be created: userdata/tenant');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/tenant', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change directory permissions of userdata/tenant');
}

// File added: userdata/tenant/info.txt
function writefile_1() {
	$fp = @fopen('userdata/tenant/info.txt', 'w');
	if ($fp === false) {
		warn('File userdata/tenant/info.txt cannot be written');
		return;
	}
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('DQpBYm91dCB0aGUgZm9sZGVyICJ1c2VyZGF0YS90ZW5hbnQiDQotLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tDQoNCkEgdGVuYW50IHVzZXMgdGhlIHNhbWUgZmlsZXMgYXMgdGhlIGJhc2Ugc3lzdGVtLA0KYnV0IGl0IGhhcyBpdHMgb3duIHVzZXJk'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YXRhLyBhbmQgdXNlcmRhdGFfcHViLw0KZW52aXJvbm1lbnQuIEhlbmNlLCB0aGUgdGVuYW50IGNhbiBoYXZlIGEgY29tcGxldGVseQ0KZGlmZmVyZW50IHBhZ2UsIGJlY2F1c2UgaXQgY2FuIHVzZSBkaWZmZXJlbnQNCmRlc2lnbnMgYW5kIGRhdGFiYXNlIHRhYmxl'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('cyBkdWUgdG8gdGhlIGluZGl2aWR1YWwNCmJhc2UgY29uZmlnLg0KDQpJZiB5b3Ugd2FudCB0byB1c2UgdGVuYW50cywgdGhlbiB5b3UgY3JlYXRlDQphIGRpcmVjdG9yeSBmb3IgZWFjaCB0ZW5hbnQgaW4gdGhpcyBkaXJlY3RvcnkuDQoNClRoZSBzdWJkaXJlY3Rv'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('cnkgbmFtZSBuZWVkcyB0byBiZSBsaWtlIHRoaXM6DQpFeGFtcGxlOiBodHRwczovL2hvc3RlZC5vaWRwbHVzLmNvbS9hYmNkZWYvDQpiZWNvbWVzOiB1c2VyZGF0YS90ZW5hbnQvaG9zdGVkLm9pZHBsdXMuY29tX19hYmNkZWYNCg0KVGhpcyBtZWFuczogSWYgdGhl'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('IHZpc2l0b3Igdml0aXMgdGhlIHBhZ2UgaHR0cHM6Ly9ob3N0ZWQub2lkcGx1cy5jb20vYWJjZGVmLw0KYW5kIHRoZSBkaXJlY3RvcnkgdXNlcmRhdGEvdGVuYW50L2hvc3RlZC5vaWRwbHVzLmNvbV9fYWJjZGVmLyBleGlzdHMsDQp0aGVuIHRoaXMgdXNlcmRhdGEg'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ZGlyZWN0b3J5IHdpbGwgYmUgY2hvc2VuIGluc3RlYWQgb2YgdXNlcmRhdGEvLg0KSWYgdGhlIHZpc2l0b3IgdmlzaXRzIGFueSBvdGhlciBVUkwsIHRoZW4gdXNlcmRhdGEvIHdpbGwgYmUgY2hvc2VuLg0K'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (is_file('userdata/tenant/info.txt') && (sha1_file('userdata/tenant/info.txt') != 'fb5838692f3d593fdede32c1b20b76688819659c')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/tenant/info.txt');
	$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/tenant/info.txt');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/tenant/info.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('userdata/tenant/info.txt', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('userdata/tenant/info.txt')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/tenant/info.txt');
} else if (sha1_file('userdata/tenant/info.txt') != 'fb5838692f3d593fdede32c1b20b76688819659c') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/tenant/info.txt');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/tenant/info.txt', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/tenant/info.txt');
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('b24vaW5mby50eHQKCnVzZXJkYXRhL2xvZ3MvKgohdXNlcmRhdGEvbG9ncy9pbmZvLnR4dAoKdXNlcmRhdGEvcHJpdmF0ZS8qCiF1c2VyZGF0YS9wcml2YXRlL2luZm8udHh0Cgp1c2VyZGF0YS9yZXNvdXJjZXMvKgohdXNlcmRhdGEvcmVzb3VyY2VzL2luZm8udHh0'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('Cgp1c2VyZGF0YS9zZWNyZXQvKgohdXNlcmRhdGEvc2VjcmV0L2luZm8udHh0Cgp1c2VyZGF0YS9zdHlsZXMvKgohdXNlcmRhdGEvc3R5bGVzL2luZm8udHh0Cgp1c2VyZGF0YS90ZW5hbnQvKgohdXNlcmRhdGEvdGVuYW50L2luZm8udHh0Cgp1c2VyZGF0YS93ZWxj'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('b21lL3dlbGNvbWUuaHRtbAohdXNlcmRhdGEvd2VsY29tZS9pbmZvLnR4dAo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('.gitignore')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: .gitignore');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('.gitignore')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .gitignore');
	} else if (sha1_file('.gitignore') != '8d4becab2ca936055320bb6af92db781a80a0622') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .gitignore');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.gitignore', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of .gitignore');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('.gitignore') !== '8d4becab2ca936055320bb6af92db781a80a0622') {
		if (@sha1_file('.gitignore') !== '198330ed5fb2e8ac221806531dfa5a064ebab104') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: .gitignore');
			$tmp = pathinfo('.gitignore');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.gitignore')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.gitignore', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('.gitignore') !== '8d4becab2ca936055320bb6af92db781a80a0622') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .gitignore');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '30fd30e4d7dfc4c997900ca78e014158542c93b4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '30fd30e4d7dfc4c997900ca78e014158542c93b4') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'cda584e156f2ea855b278031b99ee55df31d5c6a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '30fd30e4d7dfc4c997900ca78e014158542c93b4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != '2a9814a6b2b1ecc73f538d1b177a176c89d70868') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '2a9814a6b2b1ecc73f538d1b177a176c89d70868') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '2d8be37c200d5739f9191e380eb93c44ad3982f2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '2a9814a6b2b1ecc73f538d1b177a176c89d70868') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '0d7b114ba14c8c7d673870790e5819495b5a304a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '0d7b114ba14c8c7d673870790e5819495b5a304a') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '428689f4d46902cae9eb6f70c73a3fedc7161c10') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '0d7b114ba14c8c7d673870790e5819495b5a304a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('CgkJLy8gZWNobyAiXG5cbioqKioqKioqKioqKioqKioqKioqIFRlbmFudCAkdGVuYW50IC4uLlxuIjsKCQlPSURwbHVzOjpmb3JjZVRlbmFudFN1YkRpck5hbWUoJHRlbmFudCk7CgkJb2Jfc3RhcnQoKTsKCQlPSURwbHVzOjppbml0KGZhbHNlLCBmYWxzZSk7CgkJ'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YXNzZXJ0KE9JRHBsdXM6OmlzVGVuYW50KCkpOwoJCU9JRHBsdXM6Omludm9rZV9zaHV0ZG93bigpOwoJCW9iX2VuZF9jbGVhbigpOwoJfSBjYXRjaCAoRXhjZXB0aW9uICRlKSB7CgkJZndyaXRlKFNUREVSUiwgIlRlbmFudCAkdGVuYW50OiAiLiRlLT5nZXRNZXNz'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YWdlKCkuIlxuIik7CgkJJGVycm9ycysrOwoJfQp9CgpleGl0KCRlcnJvcnM+MCA/IDIgOiAwKTsKCg=='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('cron.sh')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: cron.sh');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('cron.sh')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): cron.sh');
	} else if (sha1_file('cron.sh') != '68b309f4305587d425bd599efbf928ff046d300a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): cron.sh');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('cron.sh', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of cron.sh');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('cron.sh') !== '68b309f4305587d425bd599efbf928ff046d300a') {
		if (@sha1_file('cron.sh') !== '5d0c824e233a584f7531e9576e7431dd800dc6de') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: cron.sh');
			$tmp = pathinfo('cron.sh');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('cron.sh')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('cron.sh', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('cron.sh') !== '68b309f4305587d425bd599efbf928ff046d300a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): cron.sh');
		}
	}
}

}
if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md');
	writefile_7();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md') != '1f651f10a9327646cd25d19e89fceacf1f1d589a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md') !== '1f651f10a9327646cd25d19e89fceacf1f1d589a') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md') !== '9ecd4e7ccf2be9ab32aa64409ffdc1b2db2eb238') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_7();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md') !== '1f651f10a9327646cd25d19e89fceacf1f1d589a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/oidplus_codestyle.md');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/features.html');
	writefile_8();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') != 'a9dadae35e5c974c17a9009e3bdd5e9d43ad2233') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/features.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/features.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== 'a9dadae35e5c974c17a9009e3bdd5e9d43ad2233') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== '2dde9d7e9fab7dc16c7be3146172d3326f78a3a5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/features.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/features.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/features.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/features.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_8();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== 'a9dadae35e5c974c17a9009e3bdd5e9d43ad2233') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_9();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '0902c77d63ffb51eefe5b5febda7090d2c5becf4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '0902c77d63ffb51eefe5b5febda7090d2c5becf4') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '943bbf8ade9eec87012ca395102f8fdee33b53c7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_9();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '0902c77d63ffb51eefe5b5febda7090d2c5becf4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != '73650385a9ec879918755e5482935fd56834b03b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '73650385a9ec879918755e5482935fd56834b03b') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '8b403913f8e931e0dbaec7886c6e09d6073760e7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '73650385a9ec879918755e5482935fd56834b03b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') != 'f3d68e5c4e0e8a83ab1bec39a171f081dfbe98c3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== 'f3d68e5c4e0e8a83ab1bec39a171f081dfbe98c3') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '301640d8031745c104840231a3f8b43dbb28deaa') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== 'f3d68e5c4e0e8a83ab1bec39a171f081dfbe98c3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_base.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus_base.js');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_base.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus_base.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') != '9ce2c41df321fa19e088ef66240b928c86ab4654') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_base.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus_base.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus_base.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') !== '9ce2c41df321fa19e088ef66240b928c86ab4654') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') !== '729fff144f58308ff492b70d2128e2254e26c3e9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus_base.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus_base.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus_base.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus_base.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') !== '9ce2c41df321fa19e088ef66240b928c86ab4654') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_base.js');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') != '3c344a1d3d49cb94fd2a72f7e05e3949e31d1c21') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '3c344a1d3d49cb94fd2a72f7e05e3949e31d1c21') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '2a7594a439b35d29491277dfc1b8cfc2bad8c62f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '3c344a1d3d49cb94fd2a72f7e05e3949e31d1c21') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_with_data.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_with_data.php') != '7b8a257f5adb19bb51fc405f36c6218e3a92dbe3') {

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_with_data.php') !== '7b8a257f5adb19bb51fc405f36c6218e3a92dbe3') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_with_data.php') !== '7d95e93163a83147f0c6acd137f64d69cf9416bf') {

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_with_data.php') !== '7b8a257f5adb19bb51fc405f36c6218e3a92dbe3') {

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '919d26af365f7d577b17f9fd958cb8a3090fa506') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '919d26af365f7d577b17f9fd958cb8a3090fa506') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '8e6ddfa327146cfa8e4952a875542c6c7556515e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '919d26af365f7d577b17f9fd958cb8a3090fa506') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') != '1fcc14c7fd3f56c4132ead7cd3854771aeaac0f4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== '1fcc14c7fd3f56c4132ead7cd3854771aeaac0f4') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== '773f9368b7e3752218f31a5200ea20ac13defadb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== '1fcc14c7fd3f56c4132ead7cd3854771aeaac0f4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
		}
	}
}
